Given: The web application is functioning

When: The user visits the URL

Then: The user is able to input a country for which they wish to obtain the projected population




Given: The database is updated

When: The User requests a country

Then: Display information about the projected population of that country.





Given: The database is updated

When: The User requests a country and specified a range of years

Then: Display information about the projected population of that country for the specified time period.




Given: The database is functioning

When: The Admin updates information about a country

Then: The information is available to the user




Given: The website is live

When: A user views ads on the website

Then: The admin should receive a percentage of the revenue
